<blockquote>
  <p>Binding pocket</p>
</blockquote>

<font><p>Hydrogen-bonding alignments to bound guanine in the guanine-I riboswitch, generated from PDB ID:1Y27. The bound guanine forms a Watson-Crick pair with C74. Hydrogen bonds involving 2‚Äô-OH of U22 and base edges of U47 and U51 are common to both riboswitches<sup>[4]</sup>.<br /></p></font>
